sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Reconciler
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Renderer<br/>(internal)
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Server: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (CR created/updated)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>Kustomize: Render manifests from<br/>embedded base templates
    Kustomize-->>Controller: Rendered K8s resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, SA, etc.)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Patch Deployment, Service,<br/>SA, RoleBinding, PVC, NP, PDB, HPA<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created/updated

    Note over Controller,Server: Health & Status Checks

    Controller->>Server: GET /v1/health<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    Server-->>Controller: Health status
    Controller->>Server: GET /v1/providers<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    Server-->>Controller: Provider info
    Controller->>Server: GET /v1/version<br/>8321/TCP HTTP plaintext
    Server-->>Controller: Version info
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 2: ConfigMap Change Triggered Reconciliation

    K8sAPI-->>Controller: ConfigMap watch event<br/>(llama-stack-operator-config changed)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: List LlamaStackDistributions<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Matching CRs
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Reconcile referencing CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Prometheus,RBACProxy: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>RBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Authorization result
    RBACProxy->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext (localhost)
    Controller-->>RBACProxy: Metrics response
    RBACProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics data
